[block=center][size=18]Technical[/size][/block]\
[block=automargin width=650px]\

The [url=/p/race?id=1230]roster[/url] has each stone explicitely set with its own icon and zero cost. Re-Roll cost is 1 gold in the [url=/p/ruleset?id=518]ruleset[/url] and the roster starts with three golds which can be used only for that puropse: to buy three Re-Rolls. Ruleset requires 14 players minimum for a team so each stones has to get taken.

Technically, special stones are star players in a [url=/p/race?id=1228]separate roster[/url]. A new roster gets cloned for each player which lets us to manage the player's individual special stones. The prices of special stones will be one of 25k, 50k, 75k, and 100k. The highest priced are designed to disallow a second special stone to get taken to the game.

